#. <section class="sutta" id="sn56.2"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn56.2:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 56"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 56"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn56.2:0.2"
msgid "1. Samādhivagga"
msgstr "1. Immersion"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn56.2:0.3"
msgid "2. Paṭisallānasutta"
msgstr "2. Retreat"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli5.415"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn56.2:1.1"
msgid "“Paṭisallāne, bhikkhave, yogamāpajjatha."
msgstr "“Mendicants, meditate in retreat."

msgctxt "sn56.2:1.2"
msgid "Paṭisallīno, bhikkhave, bhikkhu yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti."
msgstr "A mendicant in retreat truly understands."

msgctxt "sn56.2:1.3"
msgid "Kiñca yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti?"
msgstr "What do they truly understand?"

msgctxt "sn56.2:1.4"
msgid "‘Idaṃ dukkhan’ti yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti, ‘ayaṃ dukkhasamudayo’ti yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti, ‘ayaṃ dukkhanirodho’ti yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti, ‘ayaṃ dukkhanirodhagāminī paṭipadā’ti yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti."
msgstr "They truly understand: ‘This is suffering’ … ‘This is the origin of suffering’ … ‘This is the cessation of suffering’ … ‘This is the practice that leads to the cessation of suffering’."

msgctxt "sn56.2:1.5"
msgid "Paṭisallāne, bhikkhave, yogamāpajjatha."
msgstr "Meditate in retreat."

msgctxt "sn56.2:1.6"
msgid "Paṭisallīno, bhikkhave, bhikkhu yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti."
msgstr "A mendicant in retreat truly understands."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn56.2:2.1"
msgid "Tasmātiha, bhikkhave, ‘idaṃ dukkhan’ti yogo karaṇīyo, ‘ayaṃ dukkhasamudayo’ti yogo karaṇīyo, ‘ayaṃ dukkhanirodho’ti yogo karaṇīyo, ‘ayaṃ dukkhanirodhagāminī paṭipadā’ti yogo karaṇīyo”ti."
msgstr "That’s why you should practice meditation to understand: ‘This is suffering’ … ‘This is the origin of suffering’ … ‘This is the cessation of suffering’ … ‘This is the practice that leads to the cessation of suffering’.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn56.2:2.2"
msgid "Dutiyaṃ."
msgstr ""
